title: La La's Full Court Wedding
overview: Former MTV VJ and television personality La La Vazquez tied the knot with NBA star Carmelo Anthony in July 2010, and this series tracks all the preparations and festivities leading to the big day. It begins with La La meeting with wedding planner to the stars Mindy Weiss, and includes the bride-to-be shopping for her dress, choosing the wedding venue, planning the honeymoon and attending her bachelorette party in Las Vegas.
